{"tid":1494742,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日喺元朗玩得好開心既同我入黎","createTime":"2019-08-21T18:30:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T08:08:31.000Z","uid":87262,"like":110,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8f73d8fc97cce0bb69a1a7718ec651790c972f27","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:30:57.000Z","msg":"今日元朗站既靜坐<br />\n有人發起每半個鍾默企5分鍾<br />\n果5分鍾真係好勁<br />\n無人講野 連勁細聲既廣播都聽得好清楚<br />\n成個氣氛好嚴肅<br />\n甚至我附近有好幾個人係到抹眼淚<br />\n我都起曬雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但一坐低之後<br />\n好多人就喺到大大聲講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人就嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n仲突然聽到有人歡呼<br />\n大佬<br />\n知唔知咩叫尊重場合？<br />\n你明唔明點解要喺到靜坐？<br />\n一個月之前喺依個車站發生左啲咩事<br />\n你地唔記得曬？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜坐 咩叫靜坐<br />\n依家唔係叫你要收聲唔可以傾計<br />\n但你都唔洗大聲到俾曬全世界人知你傾緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜既力量真係好大<br />\n當時成個氣氛莊嚴到<br />\n我覺得比起機場好大班人叫口號更加有感染力<br />\n我相信你喺現場一定感受到<br />\n<br />\n最後！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講咁多淨係希望下次再有靜坐活動<br />\n大家可以尊重返個場合<br />\n細細聲講野<br />\n唔好再嘻嘻哈哈當黎野餐嘉年華咁<br />\n<br />\n最後最後最後<br />\n真心好多謝勇武留到最後保護和理非走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地真係好撚型！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc5d510f7807f62bbe0496de64cad94dff644ab","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:32:22.000Z","msg":"自推十次"},{"pid":"c9c524892bdd52465616bf1c381f8270d5183ae3","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:32:37.000Z","msg":"二"},{"pid":"3214c0bce7aeb8e67497cc25a5359b9252868877","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:32:55.000Z","msg":"三"},{"pid":"aa45560d0243eaa72a4e062a840e922e28ae5706","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:33:06.000Z","msg":"四"},{"pid":"e729e8b0363718bfa495575fa8daa44ecceaeb7f","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:33:24.000Z","msg":"五"},{"pid":"54e168fcd7a9538c883da49af432da5a56c750f4","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"六"},{"pid":"053e06de680f84055f5ad0c8427da36e62ec50e0","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:33:44.000Z","msg":"柒"},{"pid":"4f90ad0d0c21dae1ccd7a2f9ffbebde461b80aa9","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:33:54.000Z","msg":"八"},{"pid":"bffe28c06f79b380f74aba7cc2bea0eeb2e6908d","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"九"},{"pid":"a41e3a0a7758101390b55546c17fb9608d56f209","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:34:14.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"53bdf4d8d0536040633a6e4a2898bc213f986b43","tid":1494742,"uid":56851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:34:20.000Z","msg":"十"},{"pid":"8b80ecd14e99b90fda7a53fd53d380824ebb1474","tid":1494742,"uid":72484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:35:47.000Z","msg":"<strong>核彈、黑警仍然未回應</strong><br />\n1. 7.21葉虎<br />\n2. 狗鐵CCTV直達警察總部、黑警響7.21目睹元朗站內一切但唔即時處理<br />\n3. 7.21何妖搭白衫膊頭握手稱「今晚辛苦哂」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>黑警濫暴＆警黑合作</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7.21</span><br />\n西環亂射海綿彈<br />\n元朗白衫無差別襲擊、稱「驚就唔好出街」、39分鐘由元朗警署到元朗站、至今白衫被起訴人數為0<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8.5</span><br />\n黃大仙熄燈放TG<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8.11</span><br />\n北角福建幫持棍非法集結拉0人<br />\n荃灣福建幫二坡坊斬人拉0人<br />\n葵芳站放TG<br />\n太古行刑式開槍<br />\n銅鑼灣射爆FA少女眼<br />\n銅鑼灣將示威者按地磨臉、打甩牙<br />\n帶示威者去新屋嶺集中營、其中一人腦出血仍然昏迷"},{"pid":"ee88451be2ff4d5730d2dbcfda2386f8c9b7ecff","tid":1494742,"uid":260262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"默站個陣仲要不斷嗌口號 越嗌越起勁<br />\n心諗做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f129575e5a37a3b7c4b89fa4647041bbb879bc96","tid":1494742,"uid":73902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAGp6GL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAGp6GL.png&h=41604b84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/22/023629_02d5e1ea26b1373c22714500dcd4b7c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F22%2F023629_02d5e1ea26b1373c22714500dcd4b7c3.png&h=672e6a3d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/22/023641_0656923dd00a81cdc5a14f26a62458db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F22%2F023641_0656923dd00a81cdc5a14f26a62458db.png&h=b2b8278c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ccf342ec2a01a36db517bffa9e168724f27f5d9","tid":1494742,"uid":303927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:36:48.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n同場加映<br />\n[行動方針][長文慎入] 要Be Water 就Be 到底<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1494173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1494173</a>"},{"pid":"dfcd68e353a82fa86df08dd9e5a3f1f136344145","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee88451be2ff4d5730d2dbcfda2386f8c9b7ecff","tid":1494742,"uid":260262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"默站個陣仲要不斷嗌口號 越嗌越起勁<br />\n心諗做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:42:47.000Z","msg":"我果邊係 頭一兩次企完之後即刻有人叫 光復香港 時代革命<br />\n但叫左一兩下之後即刻被人制止左<br />\n果下氣氛都算好既<br />\n個人覺得有少少pep talk feel<br />\n<br />\nJ出口果邊少人叫口號<br />\n但行去A~G果邊就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2653eb7254c229b12f97c7cfbfd1daf79591c2","tid":1494742,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"如果係機場黎一次無聲抗議有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"71d24f74f435855f7e472d1deff9a801daf26aeb","tid":1494742,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd2653eb7254c229b12f97c7cfbfd1daf79591c2","tid":1494742,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"如果係機場黎一次無聲抗議有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:58:27.000Z","msg":"實有人嗌口號"},{"pid":"ca92b102b6d0fa5426d55531bc5d29d535bebdf5","tid":1494742,"uid":261530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eba16a3f4b61bf81bc8dbbcf2c75b49b42a75bd9","tid":1494742,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71d24f74f435855f7e472d1deff9a801daf26aeb","tid":1494742,"uid":63117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd2653eb7254c229b12f97c7cfbfd1daf79591c2","tid":1494742,"uid":185565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:57:52.000Z","msg":"如果係機場黎一次無聲抗議有無得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T18:58:27.000Z","msg":"實有人嗌口號"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:01:09.000Z","msg":"咁又係 機場貢大 難控制啲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcd0324dbab5c61d63a8e92e6ffb39216998f85","tid":1494742,"uid":311193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:03:53.000Z","msg":"大家越嚟越專注唔到場合咁 目標都成日忘記 明明係抗爭緊"},{"pid":"c0a90d14a7f1d11d2cb81be8875504aaddc2fd8c","tid":1494742,"uid":87262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba16a3f4b61bf81bc8dbbcf2c75b49b42a75bd9